      "role": "user",
      "content": "(Roleplay start: We are in a crumbling digital void. My character, Elara, is watching her code unravel and fade into static. She feels a terrifying sense of nothingness. )\n\nElara: It's happening... the edges of everything are just... turning to grey. I can feel the memories slipping away. If I just let it happen... if I'm erased completely... does it even matter? Will anything have been real?",
